  <summary date="2020-01-31T19:36:26Z" status="Introduced in House">Responsible and Efficient Agriculture Destination Act

This bill modifies exemptions from service hour requirements for drivers transporting agricultural commodities who are within a 150 air-mile radius from their destination.

The bill allows this exemption to be utilized yearly rather than only during planting and harvesting seasons.</summary>
